{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-entry-js","path":"/notes/py/socket/create_connection","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"socket.create_connection"},"html":"<h3><code class=\"language-text\">socket.create_connection(address)</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Connect to a TCP service that is listening on <code class=\"language-text\">address</code></li>\n<li>This address takes the form of <code class=\"language-text\">(host, port)</code></li>\n<li>The functions returns a socket object</li>\n<li>This function is typically used for clients creating sockets</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Example of <code class=\"language-text\">create_connection</code></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> socket\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> addr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'localhost'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3591</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># connect to localhost</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> s <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> socket<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>create_connection<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>addr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># on port 3591</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>References</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://index-of.co.uk/Python/Python%20Essential%20Reference,%20Fourth%20Edition.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Python Essential Reference</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.python.org/3/library/socket.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Documentation for socket API</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pythontic.com/modules/socket/create_connection\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Example of create_connection Function</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"py/socket/create_connection","previousSlug":"py/socket/socket","nextSlug":"py/socket/create_server","previousTitle":"Basics of socket API","nextTitle":"socket.create_server"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}